    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##AI in My Community: Helpful or Harmful?\r\n###Write Your Video Script\r\nNow that you’ve learned about an area of AI use related to your community and seen an example short video, write your own script for a short video that would educate viewers about this use of AI and proposes how to make AI more beneficial for all members of the community.\r\n\r\n\r\n###Do This\r\n1. Use **TaCoFoRT** to craft your prompt to AI Chat to get it help you as a collaborator on your video script.\r\n2. Go back and forth with AI chat to make the best script you can in the time you have.\r\n3. Make sure the final script that includes your input along with AI Chat's gets recorded in Part 2 of your Activity Guide\r\n\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  *Need help refining your prompt?* \r\n\r\nMake sure your video script addresses the following issues.\r\n- How do AI’s impacts differ based on who in the community is being prioritized?\r\n- How can AI be designed to benefit more people equitably?\r\n- What responsibilities do people who implement AI technologies have to address these disparities?\r\n- What are the potential environmental impacts of this AI system and how can they be mitigated?",
